"title": "6688: mercy, demonstration of God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6688: mercy, demonstration of god's",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God demonstrates his mercy in his various dealings with his people.</p>\n<h2>God as a parent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13-Ps103:14\">PSA 103:13–103:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4-Eph1:6\">EPH 1:4–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15\">ISA 49:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7-Isa63:8\">ISA 63:7–63:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:13\">ISA 66:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:17\">MAL 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2CO 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's mercy and compassion to those in distress</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:13\">ISA 49:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:23-Exod2:24\">EXO 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:14-Ps91:16\">PSA 91:14–91:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:2-Ps111:9\">PSA 111:2–111:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:7-Ps113:9\">PSA 113:7–113:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:1-Ps142:3\">PSA 142:1–142:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:9\">ISA 63:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:2\">JON 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:1\">2CO 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a></p>\n<h2>In judgment, God's mercy is just and true</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:36\">DEU 32:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:1\">PSA 143:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:3–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:18\">ISA 30:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:7-Isa54:8\">ISA 54:7–54:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:10\">ISA 60:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:2\">HAB 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>\n<h2>God may choose to show no mercy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:5\">PSA 59:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:20\">JOS 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:7\">JER 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:13\">JAS 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>God's mercy shown in his actions</h2>\n<h3>The act of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:13\">EXO 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:18\">JDG 2:18</a> <em>In the OT, salvation was seen in physical, as much as in spiritual, terms</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5\">PSA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:6-Ps28:8\">PSA 28:6–28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:21-Ps31:22\">PSA 31:21–31:22</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:10-Ps40:11\">40:10–40:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:16\">PSA 69:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15-Ps86:16\">PSA 86:15–86:16</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:2-Ps98:3\">PSA 98:2–98:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:4-Ps116:6\">PSA 116:4–116:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:27\">NEH 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:15\">2PE 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>His forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:2\">PSA 51:1–51:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18-Num14:19\">NUM 14:18–14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:6-Ps25:7\">PSA 25:6–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:8\">PSA 79:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:1-Ps130:4\">PSA 130:1–130:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:7\">ISA 55:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:4\">HOS 14:1–14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18-Mic7:19\">MIC 7:18–7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15-1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>His blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17-Deut13:18\">DEU 13:17–13:18</a></strong> <em>Moses concerning idolatry.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:12-Deut7:13\">DEU 7:12–7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:3\">DEU 30:3</a></p>",
